title: Missing Connecticut Mom of 5 Jennifer Dulos Estranged Hubby new Claim: medical bill proves my wife is alive!
itunes:title: Missing Connecticut Mom of 5 Jennifer Dulos Estranged Hubby new Claim: medical bill proves my wife is alive!
description:
Fotis Dulos' attorney says a medical bill dated after the mom of five went missing proves she is alive. Jennifer Dulos' family says it's another attempt to drag the mom's name through the mud. With Nancy Grace today discussing the case: Atlanta trial attorney Penny Douglas-Furr; forensics expert Joseph Scott Morgan; Radar Online reporter Alexis Tereszcuk; Crime Online reporter Dave Mack.
